0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"아리사","body":"그럴 리가 있냐!\n「타마야, 카기야」야!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"angry03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"episode172-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"그래, 그거!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"episode172-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"예전부터 궁금했는데……\n그거 왜 「타마야, 카기야」라고 하는 거야?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"episode172-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"아리사","body":"음~ 아마 에도시대에 「타마야」랑 「카기야」라는\n두 불꽃놀이 장인이 있었는데 불꽃놀이 관객들이 좋았던 쪽 이름을\n외쳤던 게 유래가 돼서……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"episode172-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":